works.description:
All of the photos on this page belong to 

us.  The blogger is not only using our copyrighted photos but she is  
representing our work as her own.  The photos depict Strolling Table  
costumes which we designed, built, and have been presenting at parties  
since 1999. I can prove this by providing hi-res versions of the photos
and  
other photos from the same day.  They were lifted from our site:  
www.screamingqueens.com/strolling_tables

I have sent a warning email to the blogger so it is possible that they
will  
be removed by the time you check.
